Penguin Race Adventure: Privacy policy

Welcome to the Penguin Race Adventure game for Android!

The game is available on Google Play.

Penguin Race Adventure is an offline game that stores all its data on your local device and only uses the google play services for achievements/advertisements. It does not use any user information for the game.

The game does have save and loading functionalities, which are stored on the local device and only save data required for playing the game i.e. playerstats, progress, etc. No user information is used.

If you have any further questions or concerns, please feel free to contact me on the mailadress below. 

Yours sincerely,
